intent.user_query: What is the average resolution time (in days) for service tickets, categorized by product type?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductType, AVG(CAST(ResolutionDate AS DATE) - CAST(TicketDate AS DATE)) AS AverageResolutionTime FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.ResolutionDate IS NOT NULL GROUP BY p.ProductType;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductType, AVG(CAST(ResolutionDate AS DATE) - CAST(TicketDate AS DATE)) AS AverageResolutionTime FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.ResolutionDate IS NOT NULL GROUP BY p.ProductType;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
